General.Name: Re Max Holding
General.Description: RE/MAX Holdings, Inc. operates as a franchisor of real estate brokerage services in the United States, Canada, and internationally. The company operates through three segments: Real Estate, Mortgage, and Marketing Funds. It offers real estate brokerage franchising services under the RE/MAX brand name; mortgage brokerage services to real estate brokers, real estate professionals, mortgage professionals, and other investors under the Motto Mortgage brand name; and mortgage loan processing software and services under the wemlo brand name. The company also provides BoldTrail platform, which integrates a suite of digital products that enables agents, brokers, and teams to establish, manage, and grow client relationships; and RE/MAX University platform, a learning hub designed to help each agent in their professional expertise. The company was founded in 1973 and is headquartered in Denver, Colorado.
